hadiths[9]{hadithnumber,text}:
2116,"Fateh Makka key saal main aisa bimar pada ke maut key qarib pahunch gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam meri iyaadat ko aaye to mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! merey paas bahut maal hai aur eik ladki key siwa mera koi waris nahin hai, kya main apney purey maal ki wasiyat kar dun? aap ney farmaya : '' nahin '' , mainey arz kya : do tihai maal ki ? aap ney farmaya : '' nahin '' , mainey arz kya : aadhey maal ki? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kaha : '' nahin '' , mainey arz kya : eik tihai ki? aap ney farmaya : '' eik tihai ki wasiyat karo aur eik tihai bhi bahut hai, tum apney warison ko maaldaar chhodo ye is baat sey behtar hai ke tum unko mohtaj o gharib chhod kar jaao ke wo logon key samney haath phelatey pherein , tum jo bhi kharch kartey ho is par tum ko zarur ajr milta hai, yahan tak ke us luqmey par bhi jis ko tum apni biwi key munh mein daltey ho'', mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! main to apni hijrat sey peechey reh jaaunga ? aap ney farmaya : '' tum merey baad zinda reh kar Allah ki raza-mandi ki khatir jo bhi amal karogey uski wajeh sey tumharey darjaat mein bulandi aur izafa hota jaeyga, shayad ke tum merey baad zinda raho yahan tak ke tum sey kuch qomen nafa uthaeyngi aur dusri nuqsan uthaeyngi'', ( phir aap ney dua ki) '' aey Allah ! merey Sahaba ki hijrat barqarar rakh aur ediyon key bal unhen na lota dena'' lekin becharey Saad bin khaula jin par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam afsos kartey they, (hijrat key baad) Makka hi mein unki wafat hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Saad bin abi Waqas sey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey aai hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke eik tihai sey ziyada ki wasiyat karna aadmi key liye jayez nahin hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm eik tihai sey kam ki wasiyat karney ko mustahab samajhtey hain isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eik tihai bhi ziyada hai ''."
2117,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mard aur aurat saath saal tak Allah ki itaat kartey hain phir un ki maut ka waqt aata hai aur wo wasiyat karney mein (waarison ko) nuqsan pahunchatey hain padhi. , jiski wajeh sey un dono key liye jahannam wajib ho jati hai'' , phir Abu-Hurera ney (من بعد وصية يوصى بها أو دين غير مضار وصية من الله) sey « ذلك الفوز العظيم  tak aayat padhi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- Nasar bin Ali jinhoney Ash-as bin Jabir sey riwayat ki hai wo Nasar bin Ali jahazmi key dada hain."
2118,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi musalman ko ye is baat ka haq nahin ke wo do raatein aisi haalat mein guzaarey ke wo koi wasiyat karna chahta ho aur uskey paas wasiyat tahreeri shakal mein mojud na ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees «an Zohri an Salim an ibne-Umar an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam» ki sanad sey isi tarah marvi hai."
2119,"mainey Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney wasiyat ki thi? unhoney kaha : nahin padhi. mainey puchha : phir wasiyat kaisey likhi gaee aur aap ney logon ko kis chiz ka hukm diya? ibne-Abi Aufi ney kaha : aap ney kitabullah par amal paira honey ki wasiyat ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Malik bin mighwal ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2120,"mainey hajjatul-wadaa key saal khutbey mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' Allah Taala ney har haq waley ko uska haq dey diya hai, lihaza kisi waris key liye wasiyat jayez nahin, ladka ( waladuz-zina ( bistar waley ki taraf mansub hoga ( na ke zaani ki taraf), aur zaani rajm ka mustahiq hai aur unka hisab Allah key supurd hai. jisney apney baap key ilawa kisi dusri taraf nisbat ki ya apney mawaali key ilawa ki taraf apney aap ko mansub kya is par qiyamat key din tak jari rehney wali lanat ho, koi aurat apney shohar key ghar sey uski ijazat key baghair kharch na karey '' , arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! khana bhi nahin ? aap ney farmaya : '' ye hamarey maalon mein sab sey behtar hai ''. ( yani uski ziyada hifazat honi chahiye ( phir aap ney farmaya : '' « عارية » ( mangni ( li hui chiz wapis lotaai jaeygi, « منحة  wapis ki jaeygi, qarz ada kya jaeyga, aur zamin zimmedar hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Umama key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai, 3- Ismail bin Ayash ki wo riwayat jisey wo ehale-Iraq aur ehle-Shaam sey riwayat karney mein munfarid hain, qawi nahin hai. isliye ke unhoney unsey munkar hadisein riwayat ki hain, ehale-Sham sey un ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai. isi tarah Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney kaha : 4- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : Ismail bin Ayash hadees riwayat karney key aetbar sey baqiiya sey ziyada sahih hain, baqiya ney Suqa raawiyon sey bahut si munkar hadisein riwayat ki hain, 5- Abu-Is'haq Fazari kehtey hain : Suqa raawiyon key sey baqiiya jo hadisein bayan karen usey ley lo aur Ismail bin Ayash ki hadisein mat lo , chahey wo Suqa sey riwayat karen ya ghair Suqa sey , 6- is bab mein Amr bin khaarija aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2121,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni oontni par khutba dey rahey they, us waqt mein uski gardan key nichey tha, wo jugaali kar rahi thi aur uska luaab merey kandhon key darmiyan beh raha tha, aap ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney har haq waley ka haq dey diya hai, kisi waris key liye wasiyat jayez nahin, ladka ( waladuz-zina ( bistar waley ki taraf mansub hoga, aur zaani rajm ka mustahiq hai, jo shakhs apney baap key ilawa ki taraf nisbat karey ya ( ghulam (apney malikon key ilawa ki taraf apney aap ko mansub karey unhen napasand kartey huye is par Allah ki lanat hai, Allah aisey shakhs ka na nafli ibadat qubul kerega na fariza''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : main shehar bin Hoshab ki hadees ki parwah nahin karta hun, 3- Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey Muhammad bin Ismail sey Shehar bin Hoshab key barey mein puchha to unhoney tosiq ki aur kaha : unkey barey mein ibne-Aun ney kalam kya hai, phir ibn Aun ney khud Hilal bin Abu-Zenab key wastey sey Shehar bin Hoshab sey riwayat ki hai."
2122,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney wasiyat (key nifaz) sey pehley qarz ki adaegi ka faisla farmaya , jabke tum ( Quran mein) qarz sey pehley wasiyat padhtey ho padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : aam ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke wasiyat sey pehley qarz ada kya jaeyga."
2123,"merey bhai ney apney maal key eik hissey ki merey liye wasiyat ki, mainey Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey mulaqat ki aur kaha : merey bhai ney apney maal key eik hissey ki merey liye wasiyat ki hai, aapki kya raey hai? main usey kahan kharch karun, fuqara mein, miskinon mein ya Allah ki raah mein jihad karney walon mein? unhoney kaha : meri baat ye hai ke agar tumhari jagah main hota to mujahideen key barabar kisi ko na samajhta, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jo shakhs martey waqt ghulam azad karta hai uski misal us aadmi ki tarah hai jo aasooda honey key baad hadiya karta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2124,"Barira apney zare-kitabat key barey mein un sey taawun maangney ayen aur zare-kitabat mein sey kuch nahin ada kya tha. ummul-momenin Aaisha ney un sey kaha : tum apney ghar walon key paas jaao agar wo pasand karen ke main tumhari zare-kitabat ada kar dun aur tumhari wala ( meeras (ka haq mujhey hasil ho, to main ada kar dungi . Barira ney apney ghar walon sey uska zikr kya, to unhoney inkar kar diya aur kaha : agar wo chahti hon ke tumhen azad kar key sawab hasil karen aur tumhara haq wala ( meeras ( hamarey liye ho to wo tumhen azad kar den , ummul-momenin Aaisha ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uska zikr kya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : '' usey kharido aur azad kar do isliye ke haq wala ( meeras ( usi ko hasil hai jo azad karey '' phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khadey huye aur farmaya : '' logon ko kya ho gaya hai, wo aisi shartein lagatey hain jo Allah ki kitab mein mojud nahin ? jo shakhs koi aisi shart lagaey jo Allah ki kitab ( Quran ( mein mojud nahin to wo uska mustahiq nahin hoga, agar-che wo so baar shart lagaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey aai hai. padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke azad karney waley hi ko haq wala ( meeras ( hasil hai."
